status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment:
[jdk21u-fix-request] Approval Request from Martin
Should get backported for parity with 21.0.5-oracle. The backport has been reviewed and tier 1-4 have passed.

A pull request was submitted for review.
URL: https://git.openjdk.org/jdk21u-dev/pull/715
Date: 2024-06-13 14:32:55 +0000
I think this is less important once JDK-8318889 is in, which gets the clean bailout.

Deferral Request:
Complex and incomplete fix (see follow-up fix JDK-8323274) that needs some time to stabilize. Not a regression in JDK 22.
